面性是指革命性和动摇性或者叫做不彻底性、妥协性）的阶级：既有剥削工人的一面，又有接受工人阶级及其政党领导的一面（这是1949-1956年的两面性）。因此，民族资产阶级与工人阶级的矛盾也具有两重性，既有剥削者与被剥削者的阶级利益相互对立的对抗性的一面，又有相互合作、具有相同利益的非对抗性的一面。对于工人阶级和社会主义革命来说，民族资产阶级作为一个剥削阶级是被消灭的对象，作为可以接受共产党和工人阶级领导的社会力量，又是团结和改造的对象。故C选项符合题意。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":14693,"correctTimesAmount":9078,"accuracyAmount":61.8,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":null,"newKeyType":1,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":10,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["C"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"单选","prname":"第二部分 毛泽东思想和中国特色社会主义理论体系概论>第四章 社会主义改造理论","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326234,"title":"新民主主义社会的经济成分中，完全属于社会主义性质的是（ ）","courseID":"H011901","catID":943804,"optNum":4,"a":"国营经济","b":"合作社经济","c":"个体经济","d":"国家资本主义经济","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"A","keyType":"单选","analyze":"新民主主义社会的经济成分中，完全属于社会主义性质的是国营经济。故A选项符合题意。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":14747,"correctTimesAmount":9994,"accuracyAmount":67.8,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"cr